  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TPā8">
<l>kīḻ vāṉam veḷḷeṉṟu erumai ciṟu vīṭu</l>
<l>mēyvāṉ parantaṉa kāṇ mikkuḷḷa piḷḷaikaḷum</l>
<l>pōvāṉ pōkiṉṟāraip pōkāmal kāttuṉṉaik</l>
<l>kūvuvāṉ vantu niṉṟōm kōtukalam uṭaiya</l>
<l>pāvāy eḻuntirāy pāṭip paṟai koṇṭu</l>
<l>māvāy piḷantāṉai mallarai māṭṭiya</l>
<l>tēvāti tēvaṉaic ceṉṟu nām cēvittāl</l>
<l>āvāveṉṟārāyntaruḷēlōrempāvāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As the eastern sky has dawned,</l>
<l>the buffaloes, [being] let out briefly in the morning,  have spread out to graze, look!</l>
<l>We have come and stood [here] to summon you,</l>
<l>Keeping back the remaining girls who are going, intent upon going on [to bathe].</l>
<l>O joyful lady, do get up!</l>
<l>If, singing and obtaining a paṟai-drum,</l>
<l>we go and worship</l>
<l rend="indent">Him who split [open] the horse’s jaws,</l>
<l rend="indent">the Lord of the gods who destroyed the wrestlers,</l>
<l>[He will] bless [us],</l>
<l>having examined [our demands] saying ‘ā! ā!’</l>
<l>O our maidens, accept [and] consider [this] attentively!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
